{"id": "1211559241165443122", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 19, "author_id": "1207347087369568268", "author_name": "jpzr2323", "author_bot": false, "content": "可以理解为六件套荒原狼目前是30%中毒与反击提升么", "timestamp": "2024-02-26T06:23:52.776000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1211551979457871922", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1211559911171956776", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "線上版本應該沒有效果才對。改動後最多是10%中毒與反擊提升。", "timestamp": "2024-02-26T06:26:32.518000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1207347087369568268"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1211559241165443122", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1211560336088633356", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 19, "author_id": "1207347087369568268", "author_name": "jpzr2323", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是基础伤害提升不也是等量提升中毒与反击么", "timestamp": "2024-02-26T06:28:13.826000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1211559911171956776", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
